quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  21,36,"Si …ďen yeddu…ďe nji'ii ma, …ďe njogitortaa ma si wanaa jalkitde […ďe mbi'a] "Enee, hara ko oo woni on jaŇčtotoo…óo dewetee…ói mo'on …óin?" hara kam…ďe ko …ďe yeddu…ďe jantagol jurmotoo…óo On."
  21,37,"Ne…ó…óakTagaama immorde e hawjere, aray Mi holla on Aayeeje Am …óen wata on kawju."
  21,38,"He…ďe mbi'a: "Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si tawii ko on gooŇč…óu…ďe?""
  21,39,"Sinndo …ďen yeddu…ďe ngandiino tuma tawi …ďe ittataa Yiite nge ka je'ece ma…ď…ďe wanaa kadi ka …ďabbe ma…ď…ďe kadi, kam…ďe …ďe wonaani walloytee…ďe."
  21,40,"Ko woni, nge aray e ma…ď…ďe e juhayee nge muga …ďe, hara …ďe kattantaake mdttugol nge, …ďe wonaani kadi nee…ďnoyatee…ďe."
  21,41,"GooŇč…óii Nulaa…ďe goo jalkitanooma ado maa…óa, jippii e …ďen jalkitu…ďe ko …ďe laatinoo he…ďe njalkita."
  21,42,"Maaku: "Ko hommbo reenata on jemma e √Īalawma immorde e jurmotoo…óo On, ko woni, kam…ďe gah jaŇčta Joomi ma…ď…ďe ko …ďe …óurnii…ďe."
  21,43,"Kaa no woodani …ďe rewetee…ďe …ďe no dannda …ďe gaanin Amen? ∆Āe kattantaake wallude hay woŇčkiiji ma…ď…ďe, wanaa kam…ďe ngoni wondatee…ďe immorde e Amen."
  21,44,"Ko woni, Min ndakmitii …ďee e baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen haa ngurndam …óam juutani …ďe. Enee, …ďee nji'aani won'de Menen Me…óen ara e leydi ndin Min ustira ndi immorde e seraaji mayri? Kaa ko kam…ďe ngoni fooloo…ďe …ďen."